OL,3,CNI fuel protests begin bringing major
OL,4,Croads to standstill
OL,6,FA slow-moving convoy of tractors has
OL,7,Fcaused traffic disruption in Belfast
OL,8,Fas several fuel protests are due to be
OL,9,Fheld in Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FThe traffic disruption took place near
OL,12,FBelfast City Airport, hours after the
OL,13,Fairport warned passengers there may be
OL,14,Ftraffic issues and to leave more time
OL,15,Fto travel to the airport.
OL,17,FIt comes after similar demonstrations
OL,18,Fsouth of the border disrupted fuel
OL,19,Fsupplies, port operations and traffic
OL,20,Fin Dublin city centre and on motorways
OL,21,Ffor a week.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
