OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776348651
OL,3,CNI fuel protests begin bringing major
OL,4,Croads to standstill
OL,6,FUlster Unionist leader Jon Burrows
OL,7,Fsaid there should be an emergency
OL,8,Fmeeting of the Stormont power-sharing
OL,9,FExecutive to discuss rising fuel
OL,10,Fprices.
OL,12,FHe said: "When people block roads for
OL,13,Fwhatever purpose, it has a lot of
OL,14,Funintended consequences.
OL,16,F"Right now there will be emergency
OL,17,Fservices who will struggle to get to
OL,18,Fcalls, there will be key workers who
OL,19,Fwill not be able to get to work."
