OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776348651
OL,3,CNI fuel protests begin bringing major
OL,4,Croads to standstill
OL,6,FAlthough blockades at Ireland's only
OL,7,Foil refinery and elsewhere were
OL,8,Fcleared at the weekend, smaller
OL,9,Fprotests continued on motorways around
OL,10,FDublin on Monday and a protest is due
OL,11,Fto be held at Leinster House on
OL,12,FTuesday, to coincide with a confidence
OL,13,Fvote in the government.
OL,15,FSocial media posts have called for
OL,16,Fsimilar fuel protests at several
OL,17,Flocations in Northern Ireland on
OL,18,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
