OL,3,CNI fuel protests begin bringing major
OL,4,Croads to standstill
OL,6,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill and
OL,7,Fdeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,8,FPengelly last week wrote to Prime
OL,9,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer urging him
OL,10,Fto bring forward a package of support
OL,11,Fmeasures for people in the region.
OL,13,FFuel costs have soared globally as a
OL,14,Fresult of the US-Israel war with Iran.
